1. Ja sam student na *fakultetu*. (I am a student at the faculty.)
2. Ona će *fakultet* završiti za tri godine. (She will finish the faculty in three years.)
3. Moj brat radi kao profesor na jednom *fakultetu*. (My brother works as a professor at a faculty.)
4. Većina ljudi misli da je *fakultet* nužan za uspjeh u životu. (Most people think that a faculty is necessary for success in life.)
5. *Fakultet* je bio težak, ali je vrijedio truda. (The faculty was difficult, but it was worth the effort.)
6. Bio sam na *fakultetu* kada su me zvali za posao. (I was at the faculty when they called me for the job.)
7. Nisam siguran koji *fakultet* želim upisati. (I'm not sure which faculty I want to enroll in.)
8. Ovaj *fakultet* ima odličan program za studiranje stranih jezika. (This faculty has an excellent program for studying foreign languages.)
9. Znanje koje sam stekao na *fakultetu* mi je pomoglo u poslu. (The knowledge I gained at the faculty helped me in my job.)
10. Naš *fakultet* ima mnogo međunarodnih studenata. (Our faculty has many international students.)